Class DoubleTextGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.joeclark.proceduralgeneration.DoubleTextGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RandomTextGenerator

    public class DoubleTextGenerator
extends Object
implements RandomTextGenerator
    A RandomTextGenerator which combines the output of two other RandomTextGenerators. This could be used, for example, to combine a random first name and a random last name
